# p5.js Sliding Drawing Experiment

This is an interactive drawing experiment using [p5.js](https://p5js.org/). As you draw with your mouse, the screen continuously slides, creating a unique flowing effect. The project is enhanced with inspiring background music by Oleg Mazur.

